OL,7,FA 33-year-old man has pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto sending threatening emails to a
OL,9,Ffemale MP.
OL,11,FLiam McCarthy, of Copperfield Road,
OL,12,FSouthampton, admitted "continuously"
OL,13,Fsending emails and leaving voicemails
OL,14,Ffor Caroline Nokes, Conservative MP
OL,15,Ffor Romsey and Southampton North,
OL,16,Fbetween May 15 2022 and March 4 2023.
