OL,7,FMs Hill said: "He moved on to talk
OL,8,Fabout issues he was having with the
OL,9,FDepartment of Work and Pensions and a
OL,10,Fdebt collection agency.
OL,12,F"They didn't end up seeing one another
OL,13,Fbecause the defendant cancelled his
OL,14,Fappointment because he felt unprepared.
OL,16,F"The emails continued and in August
OL,17,F2022 they started to become
OL,18,Fthreatening.
